{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":51,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"誓以播種者，"},{"SurahNumber":51,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"載重者，"},{"SurahNumber":51,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"飄流者，"},{"SurahNumber":51,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"分配者，"},{"SurahNumber":51,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"警告你們的事確是真實的，"},{"SurahNumber":51,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"報應確是要發生的。"},{"SurahNumber":51,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"以有軌道的諸天盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":51,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"你們確是各執一說的，"},{"SurahNumber":51,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"原被阻遏者，將被阻遏，而不得到達他。"},{"SurahNumber":51,"VerseNumber":10,"Text":"願常常說謊者被棄絕！"},{"SurahNumber":51,"VerseNumber":11,"Text":"他們浸沉在愚昧之中，他們是昏憒的。"},{"SurahNumber":51,"VerseNumber":12,"Text":"他們問報應日在什麼時候，"},{"SurahNumber":51,"VerseNumber":13,"Text":"那是他們在火刑上受刑之日。"},{"SurahNumber":51,"VerseNumber":14,"Text":"你們嘗試你們的刑罰吧！這就是你們要求早日實現的。"},{"SurahNumber":51,"VerseNumber":15,"Text":"敬畏的人們必定在許多樂園中，在許多泉源畔，"},{"SurahNumber":51,"VerseNumber":16,"Text":"接受他們的主所賞賜的。他們在生前確是行善的，"},{"SurahNumber":51,"VerseNumber":17,"Text":"他們在夜間只稍稍睡一下，"},{"SurahNumber":51,"VerseNumber":18,"Text":"他們在黎明時向主求饒，"},{"SurahNumber":51,"VerseNumber":19,"Text":"他們的財產中，有乞丐和貧民的權利。"},{"SurahNumber":51,"VerseNumber":20,"Text":"在大地上對於篤信的人們，有許多跡象；"},{"SurahNumber":51,"VerseNumber":21,"Text":"在你們自身中也有許多跡象，難道你們看不見嗎？"},{"SurahNumber":51,"VerseNumber":22,"Text":"在天上，有你們的給養，也有應許你們的賞罰。"},{"SurahNumber":51,"VerseNumber":23,"Text":"以天地的主盟誓，這確是真實的，猶如你們能說話一樣。"}]}